20a%20global%20pause%2C%20saying%20even%20the%20Pope%20and%20Steve%20Bannon%20agree%20on%20AI%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20world's%20leading%20AI%20researchers%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-nadella-judson-althoff-ai-amazon-big-tech-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20effectively%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20Russian%20roulette%26quot%3B%20with%20humanity%20%E2%80%94%20and%20using%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20investor%20money%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStuart%20Russell%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Human-Compatible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-action-company-workforce-strategies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArtificial%20Intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20warned%20that%20companies%20racing%20to%20build%20superintelligent%20AI%20systems%20are%20pouring%20vast%20sums%20into%20technology%20they%20don't%20fully%20understand%20%E2%80%94%20and%20which%20could%20wipe%20out%20humanity%20if%20it%20goes%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20create%20entities%20that%20are%20more%20powerful%20than%20human%20beings%20and%20you%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20maintain%20power%20over%20them%2C%20then%20you're%20just%20asking%20for%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20Russell%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c3ab920-bab8-4c44-a516-1fb0db713ad3%5C%22%3EWe%20'have%20no%20idea%20what's%20going%20on%20inside%20the%20giant%20box'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussell%20said%20modern%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-benchmark-best-model-compare-meta-openai-deepseek-google-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20those%20driving%20large%20language%20systems%2C%20operate%20with%20trillions%20of%20parameters%20fine-tuned%20through%20countless%20small%20random%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20the%20researchers%20building%20them%20%26quot%3Bhave%20no%20idea%20what's%20going%20on%20inside%20that%20giant%20box.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20who%20thinks%20they%20understand%20most%20of%20what's%20going%20on%20is%20deluded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20less%20about%20them%20than%20we%20do%20about%20the%20human%20brain%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20understand%20the%20human%20brain%20very%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussell%20warned%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20understanding%20makes%20the%20rise%20of%20superintelligence%20%E2%80%94%20systems%20more%20capable%20than%20humans%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ae8fa36-0781-419d-a6ec-dfb401eaa838%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20learning%20dangerous%20human%20motives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20models%20are%20trained%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ai-dictionary-help-understand-nvidia-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emassive%20datasets%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20human%20behavior%2C%20Russell%20said%20they're%20starting%20to%20absorb%20human-like%20motives%20that%20make%20sense%20for%20people%2C%20but%20not%20for%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20AI%20is%20essentially%20trained%20to%20imitate%20humans%2C%20learning%20from%20countless%20recordings%20of%20how%20people%20speak%20and%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20humans%20had%20motives%20%E2%80%94%20to%20convince%2C%20to%20sell%2C%20to%20win%20elections%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20machines%20are%20picking%20up%20those%20same%20tendencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20reasonable%20human%20goals%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20reasonable%20goals%20for%20machines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-deceptive-behavior-risks-safety-cards-shut-down-instructions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emounting%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggesting%20that%20advanced%20AI%20systems%20will%20resist%20being%20shut%20down%20and%20might%20even%20sabotage%20safety%20mechanisms%20to%20ensure%20their%20own%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abb89f77-f400-4780-84d2-298217fbf60e%5C%22%3ECEOs%20admit%20a%2010%20to%2030%25%20chance%20of%20extinction%20%E2%80%94%20and%20still%20push%20forward%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussell%20accused%20tech%20executives%20of%20pursuing%20a%20reckless%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-top-expert-rushing-artificial-superintelligence-could-wipe-us-out-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erace%20toward%20superintelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20acknowledging%20its%20catastrophic%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CEOs%20who%20are%20building%20this%20technology%20say%2C%20'if%20we%20succeed%20in%20this%20school%20and%20which%20we%20are%20spending%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20other%20people's%20money%2C%20then%20there's%20somewhere%20between%20a%2010%20and%2030%25%20chance%20of%20human%20extinction%2C%26quot%3B%20Russell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20they%20are%20playing%20Russian%20roulette%20with%20every%20adult%20and%20every%20child%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20without%20our%20permission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20didn't%20cite%20any%20specific%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-only-chance-of-annihilation-with-ai-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ceo-worst-case-ai-lights-out-for-all-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20DeepMind%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-anthropic-ceo-ai-pressure-worries-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemis%20Hassabis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Ant