7ca8c2737cebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20First%20Trade%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ffirst-trade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20markets%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20when%20most%20of%20the%20major%20banks%20were%20based%20in%20Manhattan's%20financial%20district%2C%20there%20was%20a%20magical%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-bankers-back-to-office-happy-hours-dining-dealmakers-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehappy%20hour%20spot%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Stone%20Street.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20city's%20efforts%20to%20turn%20the%20area%20into%20a%20nightlife%20hub%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20bankers%20would%20line%20the%20pubs%20on%20the%20cobblestoned%20street%20after%20the%20market%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20post-COVID%20world%2C%20and%20with%20many%20banks%20having%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20financial%20district%2C%20is%20the%20allure%20still%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Wednesday%20night%20in%20mid-October%2C%20I%20wandered%20down%20after%20work%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrived%20at%20around%204%3A15%20p.m.%20%E2%80%94%20admittedly%20a%20little%20early%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20fairly%20empty%20street%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20head%20to%20the%20street's%20namesake%20bar%2C%20the%20Stone%20Street%20Tavern.%20While%20the%20happy%20hour%20crowd%20that%20day%20hadn't%20yet%20trickled%20in%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bartenders%20assured%20me%20it%20would%20pick%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEncouraged%2C%20I%20took%20a%20lap%20around%20the%20street%20and%20eventually%20settled%20in%20at%20an%20Irish%20pub%20called%20Ulysses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20approached%205%3A30%2C%20the%20area%20was%20still%20pretty%20tame.%20I%20was%20starting%20to%20doubt%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20get%20the%20rambunctious%20atmosphere%20of%20old%20I%20was%20hoping%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20to%20quote%20Hemingway's%20account%20of%20the%20San%20Ferm%C3%ADn%20festival%20in%20Pamplona%2C%20Spain%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20noon%20of%20Sunday%2C%20the%206th%20of%20July%2C%20the%20fiesta%20exploded.%20There%20is%20no%20other%20way%20to%20describe%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroups%20of%20people%20began%20to%20descend%20onto%20Stone%20Street%2C%20filling%20the%20empty%20tables.%20Some%20walked%20around%20with%20their%20eyes%20glued%20to%20sheets%20of%20paper%2C%20periodically%20looking%20up%2C%20like%20they%20were%20reading%20a%20map.%20I%20approached%20one%20of%20the%20small%20groups%20and%20asked%20what%20was%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20a%20scavenger%20hunt%20with%20our%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20them%20told%20me.%20They%20worked%20for%20one%20of%20the%20stock%20exchange%20firms%20in%20the%20city%20and%20were%20out%20on%20a%20team-building%20excursion%2C%20with%20Stone%20Street%20being%20one%20of%20the%20must-see%20stops%20in%20FiDi.%20While%20the%20group%20wasn't%20exactly%20down%20there%20to%20stay%20for%20happy%20hour%20that%20particular%20night%2C%20they%20said%20Stone%20Street%20was%20one%20of%20a%20few%20watering%20holes%20they%20frequent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20told%20me%20that%20at%20his%20old%20job%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tradition%20to%20bring%20new%20hires%20to%20Stone%20Street%20on%20their%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20from%20New%20York%20originally%2C%20so%20I%20got%20to%20feel%20the%20whole%20finance%20scene%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20they%20had%20to%20get%20on%20with%20their%20scavenger%20hunt%2C%20so%20I%20wandered%20back%20to%20Ulysses%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20group%20of%20guys%20in%20their%20classic%20finance%20vests%20clanking%20their%20one-liter%20Oktoberfest-style%20beers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20begun%20to%20get%20dark%20now%2C%20and%20the%20street%20was%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stone%20street%20nyc%20happy%20hour%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690126c2599d46a4ccc10684%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Edwards%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20walked%20into%20Ulysses%2C%20a%20gregarious%20group%20of%20analysts%20(also%20in%20vests)%20from%20a%20large%20data%20house%20looked%20like%20they%20were%20having%20a%20ball%2C%20pints%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20them%20I%20was%20working%20on%20a%20story%20about%20Stone%20Street%2C%20they%20were%20eager%20to%20contribute.%20One%20said%20his%20colleagues%20at%20his%20old%20currency%20exchange%20firm%20nearby%20used%20to%20%26quot%3Blive%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20particular%20bar%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20that%20the%20whole%20street%20would%20be%20regularly%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPre-COVID%2C%20this%20whole%20area%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20you%20could%20not%20get%20a%20single%20bench%2C%20you%20couldn't%20walk%20into%20a%20bar%20physically.%20It%20was%20like%20Woodstock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20While%20it's%20not%20back%20to%20that%20level%20yet%2C%20it's%20improving%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIs%20it%20better%20than%20'22%2C%20'23%3F%20Yes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20regaling%20me%20with%20some%20of%20their%20old%20stories%2C%20we%20chatted%20a%20while%20about%20the%20market%20and%20about%20must-read%20finance%20books%3A%20Two%20they%20recommended%20include%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20Learned%20Losing%20a%20Million%20Dollars%26quot%3B%20by%20Jim%20Paul%20and%20Brendan%20Moynihan%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BReminiscences%20of%20a%20Stock%20Operator%26quot%3B%20by%20Edwin%20Lefevre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20animated%20evening.%20People%20seemed%20to%20be%20having%20a%20good%20time%20with%20their%20colleagues%2C%20and%20everyone%20I%20chatted%20with%20was%20in%20a%20jovial%20mood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20told%20the%20analysts%20that%20I%20had%20to%20head%20home%2C%20they%20pleaded%20with%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20have%20at%20least%20%3Cem%3Eone%3C%2Fem%3E%20round%20with%20us!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20obliged%2C%20getting%20an%20Oktoberfest%20lager.%20Taking%20a%20sip%20of%20the%20pint%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20deny%20that%20the%20magic%20was%20indeed%20still%20alive%20and%20well%20on%20the%20old%20Manhattan%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20are%20your%20favorite%20happy%20hour%20spots%20to%20visit%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Afirsttrade%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELet%20us%20know%3C%2Fa%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappy-hour-spots-nyc-wall-street-bars-nightlife-stone-street-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761730502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69010d44c007ca8c2737ca68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappy-hour-spots-nyc-wall-street-bars-nightlife-stone-street-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20post-COVID%20world%2C%20and%20with%20many%20banks%20having%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20financial%20district%2C%20is%20Stone%20Street's%20allure%20still%20there%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappy-hour-spots-nyc-wall-street-bars-nightlife-stone-street-